Auto detect text files and normalize line endings to LF

text=auto eol=lf

Windows files
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
Documents
*.md text
*.txt text
Scripts
*.sh text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf
Configs
*.json text
*.yaml text
*.yml text
*.toml text
Source code
*.ts text
*.tsx text
*.js text
*.jsx text
*.css text
*.scss text
*.html text
Binary files
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.mov binary
*.mp4 binary
*.mp3 binary
*.flv binary
*.fla binary
*.swf binary
*.gz binary
*.zip binary
*.7z binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.pdf binary